Title: Dionysus in '69
Actors: Remi Barclay, Samuel Blazer, Jason Bosseau, Richard Dia
Plot: Filmed stageplay based on the ancient greek play The Bacchae written by Euripides. This play is performed by members of The Performance Group, an NYC experimental theater group who has made their own personal adaptation of this ancient text. Filmed by Brian DePalma.
